(1373, 'corbus1', '\\xa0\\x4d\\xbb\\x9e\\x34\\x30\\xbf\\x7b\\x9d\\x5c\\xc5\\xd9\\xbd\\xe9\\x20\\xde', , '2005-08-25 04:34:28', '2005-08-30 07:05:50', 1, 1, 'rmg@corbus.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'charu', '0120', '2567030', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Established in 1994, Corbus an ISO 9001:2000 certified organization has been at the helm of providing consulting, IT, and BPO services to its global clientele for about a decade. Corbus IT and BPO services effectively respond to the rapidly changing global business environment. Focused on building long term relationships, Corbus enables you to capture market opportunities and consolidates your leadership position by:\r\n\r\n Undertaking strategic business initiatives\r\n Enhancing business efficiency and productivity\r\n Improving time to market\r\n\r\nOur services are focused at adding value to the efficiency of your esteemed enterprise while working within your budget and schedule. We strive to improve the flow and management of your data to strengthen your bottom line. \r\n\r\n\r\nOUR VISION\r\nRecognized Centers of Excellence providing cost-effective IT and BPO services.\r\n\r\n\r\nCorbus provides its clients a wide spectrum technology and service base through experienced professionals with multiple platform skills and rich domain experience in various industry segments. Client trust is reinforced by Corbuss strong project management capabilities. \r\n\r\nCorbus clients derive the benefit of its flexible business model that provides them integrated services through optimal delivery and pricing patterns, with highest service quality on time. Corbus is an affiliate of Soin International  a Dayton, Ohio based high technology, multi-faceted organization. Corbus caters to its global clientele through its offices in Europe, India, and US. \r\n\r\n\r\nSOIN INTERNATIONAL\r\nCorbus is a wholly owned subsidiary of Soin International, LLC, a multinational holding company that provid