ct management capabilities. \r\n\r\nCorbus clients derive the benefit of its flexible business model that provides them integrated services through optimal delivery and pricing patterns, with highest service quality on time. Corbus is an affiliate of Soin International  a Dayton, Ohio based high technology, multi-faceted organization. Corbus caters to its global clientele through its offices in Europe, India, and US. \r\n\r\n\r\nSOIN INTERNATIONAL\r\nCorbus is a wholly owned subsidiary of Soin International, LLC, a multinational holding company that provide strategic management and financial services to its diverse array of subsidiaries and affiliates. The Soin International subsidiary companies provide a variety of high-tech solutions, engineering services, and manufactured product.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe founder, chairman and chief executive officer of Soin International is Rajesh K. Soin who believes that the best investments are in bright, dedicated people. This philosophy means the entrepreneurs who manage the Soin International family of companies are free to provide the highest level of service to their customers.\r\n\r\nThe most prominent success among Mr. Soin''s investments is the first, Modern Technologies Corp., now known as MTC Technologies, Inc. (MTCT). Founded in 1984, MTC and its afiliates now employ more than a thousand people worldwide. It is also listed on the NASDAQ stock exchange.', 4, 'Senior HR Executive', '', 0, 'Corbus India Pvt Ltd', 'Corbus India Pvt. Ltd.\r\nSDF # C-5\r\nSoftware Technology Park\r\nNoida Special Economic Zone\r\nNoida - 201305\r\nIndia\r\nTel: +91-120-256 7030\r\nFax: +91-120-256 7040', 'IN', 'DL', 549, '', 2, 28, 7, 6, 5, 3, 22, 'www.corbus.com', '', '', '');
