(1248, 'sylantrojobs', '\\x29\\x86\\xb5\\x97\\xd7\\x5d\\x35\\xc6', , '2005-08-19 02:19:07', '2005-08-19 02:19:07', 1, 1, 'jobsindia@sylantro.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '2011-04-26 10:12:13', 0, 'Velu.C', '080', '51261601', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '080', '51261602', '', 'About Sylantro Systems Corp.\r\nSylantro Systems Corp. (Sylantro for short) provides the premier software platform for advanced Hosted PBX and IP Centrex services for business, residential, wireless and other applications. Sylantro is the market leader in hosted PBX and IP Centrex deployments. With a unique combination of advanced applications, a carrier-class platform, and proven go-to- market services, Sylantro allows service providers to rapidly deliver high-value, high-margin managed telephony services.  These award-winning solutions offer the end users sophisticated communications services without the cost and complexity of today??s in-house PBX and key systems.\r\n\r\nSylantro is a privately held company backed by premier investors. Sylantro India is a fully owned subsidiary of Sylantro Systems Corporation, USA. For more information about Sylantro, visit our Web site, www.sylantro.com.\r\n\r\nSylantro India\r\nSylantro Software India Pvt. Ltd. was founded in December 2003, and started out as a development center in Bangalore. It has matured into a complete product development, quality assurance, field operations, technical support and professional services. This highly motivated, dynamic group collectively has over 100 years of product development, implementation, custom development, support and testing experience. The core engineering team in India comprises of engineers from the parent company. We are now expanding our Indian team in all the above mentioned areas and are looking for people with a can-do attitude who want to grow this group to be one of the best in the world.  \r\n\r\nSylantro Software India Pvt Ltd.\r\n1st Floor, Uma Admiralty\r\nNo.1, Bannerghatta Road\r\nBangalore