ctively experimented with various business models and accomplished the rare feat of providing an array of world-class services to satiate the needs of different consumer segments in the Internet space. From Matrimony, Property, Automobile, Jobs to Listings and SMS services, the group has over 15 million users worldwide and is widely accepted as the undisputed leader in the Indian Internet space.\r\n\r\nToday Consim Info has investments from global venture capital moguls like Yahoo, Canaan Partners and Mayfield Fund in its repertoire, and has charted out ambitious plans for its expansion by setting up operations in the US, UK and in other countries and is also looking forward to promoting globally the verticals that it manages in the Internet and mobile industry.\r\n', 2, 'Sr. Mgr. HR', '', 6, 'Consim Info Pvt. Ltd.', 'No:94, TVH Beliciaa Towers, \r\n10th Floor, Tower 2, \r\nMRC Nagar, Mandaveli, \r\nChennai - 600 028, \r\nTamilnadu, India. ', 'IN', 'TN', 540, '', 2, 30, 6, 0, 6, 4, 22, 'http://www.consim.com', '', '/home/es/esLogos/201006/22/16/nirmala_1.gif', '');
