rgan Stanley, SAP, Hewlett-Packard, WalMart, Sun Microsystems, Cisco, Ericsson, Nokia, etc., to whom we provide diversified services like Multilingual Content Management, Localization, E-learning, Application Development and Maintenance, Bespoke Solutions, Testing and ERP\r\n(PeopleSoft Enterprise). Our VeriTest division is the world''s largest independent testing organization.', 47, 'Manager - Recruitment', 'josephine.ramya@lionbridge.com', 0, 'L10NBRIDGE Technologies', 'Spectra, Hiranandani Gardens, Powai, Mumbai 400 076, India', 'IN', 'MM', 541, '', 2, 28, 6, 2, 7, 3, 22, 'http://www.lionbridge.com', '', '', ''),
