enior management. We serve to more than 50 clients from all over the world.\r\nWe are a team of 10 professionals having sourcing experience in various industries like Information Technology, manufacturing, marketing. The organisation is headed by Mr.S.Ganesan who has over 22 years of experience in spanning over the wide spectrum of industries ranging from FMCG, Office Automation, and Resourcing. He has been in the executive search field for the last 12 years', 0, 'Business Head', '', 0, 'Millenniums Management & Executive Search Consultants', '2C, FIRST FLOOR,\r\nMAHESWARI APARTMENTS,\r\n76, T.M.MAISTRY STREET,\r\nTHIRUVANMIYUR,\r\nCHENNAI- 600041', 'IN', 'TN', 540, '', 1, 21, 6, 7, 3, 1, 22, 'www.jobspoint.com', '', '', ''),
